,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev62-ep3-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"摩卡，你那個桌遊還滿強的對吧？\n因為有用骰子，明明就很有運氣因素的說","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev62-ep3-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"摩卡","body":"呵呵呵～。我有秘密的訣竅唷～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"niyaniya01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"ev62-ep3-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"那個桌遊嗎……？\n但是，因為完全贏不了摩卡，是不是還加了特別規則\n只有摩卡骰的數字要-1之類的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev62-ep3-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"摩卡","body":"那個規則，還真是嚴苛啊～。\n真過分呢～，大家","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"ev62-ep3-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"但就算這樣你也還是贏很多吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev62-ep3-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"摩卡","body":"呵呵～。對啊～。因為大家太弱啦～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"niyaniya01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"ev62-ep3-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"好的好的。\n總覺得很狡猾耶","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev62-ep3-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"……禮物收到可以大家一起玩的玩具，\n那還是第一次","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev62-ep3-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWind